The validity of the included studies was assessed using the Critical Appraisal Skills Program (CASP) tool for the cohort studies and Center for Evidence Based Management (CEBMa) for the cross sectional studies.11,12 These tools consisted of several checklist based on the research methods used and were used to assess the trustworthiness, relevance, and results of the published papers.Results
